    "Federated learning for distributed WSNs with cloud integrationThis system utilizes FL to detect anomalies in distributed WSNs that integrate with the cloud.",
    "It enables model training to be done collaboratively across multiple sensor nodes without the sharing of raw data.",
    "The cloud server plays a central role in aggregating the local model updates from individual nodes to create a global model for anomaly detection.",
    "The global ML model, known as θg, is initialized on the cloud server."
